    grid-row: span 2;
    grid-column: span 3;
}
```

**4. Grid Area (Named Areas):**
```css
.item {
    grid-area: row-start / col-start / row-end / col-end;
}
```

**5. Grid Area with Named Areas:**
```css
.container {
    grid-template-areas:
        "header header header"
        "sidebar main main"
        "footer footer footer";
}

.item {
